  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THIS GAME</h2>Violation is a First Person Horror Game that takes Place in many other Worlds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783310/extras/5a0ea70657caf999ae75e7fd3028b741.avif?t=1666890413\" width=600 height=350 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2>You got lost in a Forest. Now you search a Way back to the road....But while you are searching the way back, something is happening, something that isnt even real anymore. A Monster came up and attacked you. Now you try to Escape the Monster and find the Way back to the Road to Escape that Place.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783310/extras/2644867f31ab2085a9c6d2f4e2e89546.avif?t=1666890413\" width=600 height=350 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2>- Jumpscares<br><br>- Puzzles<br>- Inventory System<br>- Horror Atmosphere<br>- AI",
